,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>deuter futura pro 38</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好細</blockquote><br />\n唔鐘意50l以上，愈大只會帶得愈多無謂野</blockquote><br />\n其實係好啱<br />\n好多時啲人頭幾次backpacking就係因為個袋大 越帶越多無謂唔等洗嘅嘢<br />\n最後只會係自己辛苦<br />\n樓主你或者考慮下exos 48/58<br />\n因為個袋比好多傳統backpack輕好多"},{"pid":"ae547e75e838119548807e931f7bd9ad5fa117b2","tid":44280,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾L?帶到幾日野？</blockquote><br />\n我呢個S/M裝到24L<br />\nM/L裝到26L<br />\n去日本接近3星期都係用呢個"},{"pid":"0704326a875ea0ffc9dba184652139c98085dd67","tid":44280,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>deuter futura pro 38</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好細</blockquote><br />\n唔鐘意50l以上，愈大只會帶得愈多無謂野</blockquote><br />\n斷背兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f33b46164b683b83c92f40fe24b21bcbdfd691","tid":44280,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"想問邊到osprey多款揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fb43beb61d5323ac315ee441a35ddee98baea6","tid":44280,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想買backpack但冇經驗<br />\n先了解大家用開咩背囊有咩好處<br />\n平時行山露營用開Osprey<br />\n睇中Osprey Arther 70<br />\n希望放到一至二人既日用品</blockquote><br />\naether 嚟緊會update條line<br />\n新款嘅aether係冇得換唔同size嘅hipbelt同hardness<br />\n呢方面注意下<br />\n<br />\n平時都係用開aether60 但已經開始想換</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁姐係要趁早買<img 