class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打算買黎去東南亞用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3d80be10bdabd80a83eaec11c4cb4e2df87c22","tid":44280,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過一次backpack去旅行<br />\n<br />\n最煩係底褲同襪 又唔一定到到有洗衣機<br />\n<br />\n大家backpacker點解決依個問題<br />\n<br />\n利申40L好似都夠用<br />\n<br />\n不過一到春季去唔可以日日著同一套衫就未必可行<br />\n<br />\n黎緊四月會去四國, 仲要行山踏單車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n底褲同襪帶多幾套啦<br />\n好唔係佔好多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b331cc24ef42aecc39f4681431472d7ad5e0c37","tid":44280,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過一次backpack去旅行<br />\n<br />\n最煩係底褲同襪 又唔一定到到有洗衣機<br />\n<br />\n大家backpacker點解決依個問題<br />\n<br />\n利申40L好似都夠用<br />\n<br />\n不過一到春季去唔可以日日著同一套衫就未必可行<br />\n<br />\n黎緊四月會去四國, 仲要行山踏單車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHostel實有洗衣機嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未必既，不過其實可以手洗，我環台個時都係手洗，<br />\n帶D快乾衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e93148b590de8b600058c0fa43d1d35f41d881","tid":44280,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過一次backpack去旅行<br />\n<br />\n最煩係底褲同襪 又唔一定到到有洗衣機<br />\n<br />\n大家backpacker點解決依個問題<br />\n<br />\n利申40L好似都夠用<br />\n<br />\n不過一到春季去唔可以日日著同一套衫就未必可行<br />\n<br />\n黎緊四月會去四國, 仲要行山踏單車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n底褲同襪帶多幾套啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">又</span>唔係佔好多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"73588b01a11e13c419d787552252658b04ab7b7f","tid":44280,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打點睇Osprey KESTREL 48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打算買黎去東南亞用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一個人又唔帶太多野應該夠<br />\n東南亞都唔會玩十日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baa88ceb33bc1b1078e00b60b8d06b1976d9951","tid":44280,"uid":34113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"mystery ranch 3 day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14jpzPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14jpzPL.jpg&h=75ebc3bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e21508770643ed430646719e0bfc20be9be881d8","tid":44280,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打點睇Osprey KESTREL 48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打算買黎去東南亞用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一個人又唔帶太多野應該夠<br />\n東南亞都唔會玩十日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最主要都係擺衫仲有相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未試過做backpacker 好緊張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪都係日頭用個細嘅backpack擺下水呀相機 然後將呢個大嘅放喺hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf9c94af80ac7923413c669544b0a7dd9edd356","tid":44280,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"有個Osprey Aether 60都幾正 唔知幾錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我諗上唔到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907ee47c2a9248ce4775e3d59adf1e5649baf526","tid":44280,"uid":20535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"osprey redial 26<br />\n<br />\n咩太大好累架"},{"pid":"044cd721eace19e6bbc599d11ec5f573a74e74cc","tid":44280,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"