"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/021149_38431767589855e598df4c2e212ebd7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F021149_38431767589855e598df4c2e212ebd7e.jpg&h=d5e10eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上唔到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3982a4e449ea3836e738a8b79894898f83b3c8c5","tid":44280,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835cb634a9eb97378b8060ac846719d845311004","tid":44280,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affd3e2e03295e1bb5ae01ab94c682cb538630f9","tid":44280,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"見有啲人去得十日八日仲要係市區<br />\n但個袋仲高過自己個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己純粹睇景唔買嘢<br />\n開頭用40L都係嫌太大太麻煩<br />\n<br />\n而家用呢個<br />\n超輕好方便<br />\n有埋網底唔會焗<br />\n帶幾套衫褲加件褸<br />\n城市嘅話留一頭半個月都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.twenga.com/deportes/mochila-de-montana/mochila-ultra-hiker-15-tp_4102019473932438108f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.twenga.com%2Fdeportes%2Fmochila-de-montana%2Fmochila-ultra-hiker-15-tp_4102019473932438108f.jpg&h=5eda14e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d213d83a360957e8a84deeb0d9ce696aa1c9b2c3","tid":44280,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過一次backpack去旅行<br />\n<br />\n最煩係底褲同襪 又唔一定到到有洗衣機<br />\n<br />\n大家backpacker點解決依個問題<br />\n<br />\n利申40L好似都夠用<br />\n<br />\n不過一到春季去唔可以日日著同一套衫就未必可行<br />\n<br />\n黎緊四月會去四國, 仲要行山踏單車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n底褲同襪帶多幾套啦<br />\n好唔係佔好多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我指緊係出面D衫冬天就可以唔換, 春天仲要做運動就一定要換<br />\n雖然日本春天同香港冬天差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又踩車又行山緊係愈輕便愈好啦<br />\n帶少啲衫褲<br />\n至好淨係帶快乾嘅款<br />\n寧願勤啲洗<br />\n<br />\n正常hostel同business hotel會有洗衣機<br />\n擔心嘅話可以問清楚先book<br />\n慳啲嘅手洗都得"},{"pid":"758e73b1540b74ee8c55624fcc9768ad74a83133","tid":44280,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打點睇Osprey KESTREL 48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打算買黎去東南亞用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一個人又唔帶太多野應該夠<br />\n東南亞都唔會玩十日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最主要都係擺衫仲有相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未試過做backpacker 好緊張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪都係日頭用個細嘅backpack擺下水呀相機 然後將呢個大嘅放喺hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎個細嘅backpack(&lt;20L)去可以當埋daypack用<br />\n除非野外求生幾個月<br />\n如果唔係唔好做咕哩<br />\n<br />\n我自己就拎個15L backpack<br />\n再摺埋一個薄身gregory斜咩袋放入去<br />\n其實自己帶嘢唔多<br />\n全日咩住個backpack都唔覺辛苦<br />\n不過有啲場合咩backpack唔係咁合適<br />\n有多個斜咩就方便好多"},{"pid":"8a95868c2ac7a3d6261bb8b1bc5f17effb1a24c5","tid":44280,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一個人又唔帶太多野應該夠<br />\n東南亞都唔會玩十日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最主要都係擺衫仲有相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未試過做backpacker 好緊張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪都係日頭用個細嘅backpack擺下水呀相機 然後將呢個大嘅放喺hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎個細嘅backpack(&amp;lt;20L)去可以當埋daypack用<br />\n除非野外求生幾個月<br />\n如果唔係唔好做咕哩<br />\n<br />\n我自己就拎個15L backpack<br />\n再摺埋一個薄身gregory斜咩袋放入去<br />\n其實自己帶嘢唔多<br />\n全日咩住個backpack都唔覺辛苦<br />\n不過有啲場合咩backpack唔係咁合適<br />\n有多個斜咩就方便好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係唔想拎多袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過換酒店要再pack應該好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cf06de9b935d666e3c0030a665f9d9aa15704c","tid":44280,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gw.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/45136928/TB2JoguaXXXXXXXXpXXXXXXXXXX_!!45136928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgw.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi1%2F45136928%2FTB2JoguaXXXXXXXXpXXXXXXXXXX_%21%2145136928.jpg&h=0a111d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貪靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重係重D, 但都防水防雪<br />\n背負系統又有專利"}]}